"{\"uid\": \"cnbc.com-2024-07-31-simone-biles-credits-therapy-for-her-success-at-the-paris-olympics.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Related Stories  There is one thing that Simone Biles credits for her return to the Olympics this year: therapy.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles is now themost decorated U.S. Olympic gymnast in historywith eight Olympic medals.\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And she says it would not have been possible without consistent mental health support.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being in a good mental spot, seeing my therapist every Thursday is kind of religious for me.\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So that's why I am here today,\\\" Biles said in aninterviewwith NBC News last month.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9913625527456154, \"rank\": 0.008618091543565201, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The road to victory wasn't an easy one for Biles.\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years ago,she withdrew from the team gymnastics competitionat the postponed 2020 Tokyo Olympics citing mental health concerns.\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She later explained that she was experiencing what gymnasts refer to as \\\"the twisties.\\\"\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although the twisties is not an official medical diagnosis, the experience is used to describe a psychologically-perceived disconnection between a gymnast's mind and their body as they are performing, especially during twists.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The effects of the twisties can range from missing twists or twisting more than one planned to, and landing or falling in a way that can cause injury.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When Biles was completing an Amanar vault at the 2020 Olympics, she noticeably turned 1.5 twists instead of the usual 2.5.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1152, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8120384880063897e-40, \"text\": \"Amanar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even onlookers noticed that sheseemed disoriented during the twist.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have to focus on my mental health,\\\" Bilessaidafter pulling out of the Olympics in 2021.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not trust myself as much anymore.\\\"\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles regained that trust within herself by starting small through practicing on soft surfaces and in ball pits,she shared via Instagram.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.721748686681382e-20, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She trained extremely hard ahead of the Paris Olympics and would sometimes leave practice feeling defeated because she experienced the twisties again, she toldNBC.\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But she did not give up because \\\"I do not want to be down the road in 10 years, look back, and be like, 'Oh, I wish I would have tried,\\\" she told NBC.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1897, \"end\": 1900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999658862391626, \"rank\": 3.267947426523773e-05, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles kept practicing and attending her weekly therapy sessions and began to feel more in tune with her body as she performed.\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday, theTeam USA gymnastics team won goldin the Olympic women's team final, and Biles made history as a result.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I always rise to the occasion,\\\" Biles said in an episode of herNetflix documentary, \\\"Simone Biles Rising,\\\" which was released this month.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even after all of the traumas and the downfalls, I have always risen.\\\"\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Want to stop worrying about money?Sign up for CNBC's new online courseAchieve Financial Wellness: Be Happier, Wealthier & More Financially Secure.\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2408, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 1.2601648727299153e-11, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will teach you the psychology of money, how to manage your stress and create healthy habits, and simple ways to boost your savings, get out of debt and invest for the future.\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Start today and use code EARLYBIRD for an introductory discount of 30% off through September 2, 2024.\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus,sign up for CNBC Make It's newsletterto get tips and tricks for success at work, with money and in life.\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2807, \"end\": 2811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 1.2601648727299153e-11, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get Make It newsletters delivered to your inbox  Learn more about the world of CNBC Make It  \\u00a92025Versant Media, LLC.\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 3018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2980, \"end\": 2984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 1.2601648727299153e-11, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}, {\"begin\": 3014, \"end\": 3017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9999754921459115, \"rank\": 2.450845462373452e-05, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Versant Media Company\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3043, \"end\": 3050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\", \"score\": 0.9999939305948845, \"rank\": 5.110614197408476e-06, \"text\": \"Versant\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\"}]}]}"